%^RESET%^%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Prestige Class
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Versatile Arcanist:

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Requirements:%^RESET%^ Level 40 Character
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^             %^RESET%^ Level 20 Sorcerer
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^             %^RESET%^ 20 Points Spent in the Spellcraft Skill
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^             %^RESET%^ 20 Base Charisma (before equipment modifiers)

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Races allowed:%^RESET%^ human, half-elf, half-orc, half-drow, elf, 
               drow, halfling, gnome, voadkyn, kobold, goblin, 
               orc (tanarukk), yuan-ti

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Alignments allowed:%^RESET%^ any
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Cannot multiclass with:%^RESET%^ mage, psion, psywarrior
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Hitdice:%^RESET%^ d6
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Saving throws:%^RESET%^ will strong, fort/reflex weak
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Class Skills:%^RESET%^ academics, disguise, influence, spellcraft
              **disguise temporarily substituted to perception until installed

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Class Feats:%^RESET%^
   %^RESET%^L1: greater spell knowledge
   %^RESET%^L4: master of elements
   %^RESET%^L7: master of versatility

Versatile arcanists have a flexible understanding of the weave that only
rare sorcerers ever truly obtain.  Such mastery of arcana extends not only
to the sorcerer's instinctive understanding of magic and magical items, 
but also grants a command of spells that most normal sorcerers never 
manage to learn.

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^See also: %^RESET%^feats, skills, spells, cast, prepare, master